<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h2 style="color: #7B2FBE;">Thanks for applying to Suppova, <%= @worker.first_name %>!</h2>
  <p>We've received your application and compliance documents. Our team will review them shortly.</p>
  <p>Most applications are reviewed within 1–2 business days. You'll get a notification in the app once a decision has been made.</p>
  <p>If it's been a while and you haven't heard back, you can message us directly:</p>
  <p style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
    <a href="<%= @messages_url %>" style="background: #7B2FBE; color: white; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Message Suppova Support</a>
  </p>
  <p style="color: #888; font-size: 13px;">— The Suppova Team</p>
</body>
</html>
